óŔQarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/plugin_rm.mdŔ@1953e26af210ca26876c5d7979f5a3904b0b6ea308aa820efacb46cf8ed9ce3aįtitle: plugin rmĎ•NotesŕĚThis does not remove the plugin commands from the current scope or from 
``plugin list``
 in the current shell. It instead removes the plugin from the plugin

registry file (by default, 
``$nu.plugin-path``
). The changes will be apparent the

next time 
``nu``
 is launched with that plugin registry file.
This can be useful for removing an invalid plugin signature, if it can't be

fixed with 
``plugin add``
.
íźźŕ Title: title: plugin rm
Path: Notes
Content:
This does not remove the plugin commands from the current scope or from 
``plugin list``
 in the current shell. It instead removes the plugin from the plugin

registry file (by default, 
``$nu.plugin-path``
). The changes will be apparent the

next time 
``nu``
 is launched with that plugin registry file.
This can be useful for removing an invalid plugin signature, if it can't be

fixed with 
``plugin add``
.
